statements: SELECT * FROM telehealth_studies;
SELECT study_id, study_name, patient_gender, patient_age FROM telehealth_studies WHERE patient_condition = 'Diabetes';
SELECT study_name, patient_age FROM telehealth_studies WHERE patient_id = 12345;
SELECT * FROM telehealth_studies WHERE data_collected = true ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT study_name, patient_id, patient_condition FROM telehealth_studies WHERE patient_age > 50 ORDER BY study_name ASC
SELECT * FROM telehealth_studies WHERE data_collected = TRUE;
SELECT study_name, study_description, start_date, end_date FROM telehealth_studies WHERE patient_gender = 'F' ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT study_name, patient_id, patient_condition FROM telehealth_studies WHERE patient_age > 50 AND patient_gender = 'M';
SELECT DISTINCT(patient_condition) FROM telehealth_studies WHERE data_collected = TRUE AND patient_age < 30;
SELECT study_id, study_name, start_date, end_date FROM telehealth_studies WHERE patient_condition LIKE '%diabetes%' ORDER BY study_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM Patients;
SELECT patient_name, age FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM Patients WHERE age > 50;
SELECT patient_name, medical_history FROM Patients WHERE medical_history IS NOT NULL;
SELECT result_id, study_id, patient_id, study_date FROM StudyResults WHERE study_date > '2022-01-01';

SELECT patient_id, patient_name, age, gender FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Female' ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT patient_name, age, medical_history FROM Patients WHERE age >= 50 AND medical_history IS NOT NULL;

SELECT patient_name, gender, study_date FROM Patients INNER JOIN StudyResults ON Patients.patient_id = StudyResults.patient_id WHERE StudyResults.study_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY study_date DESC;

SELECT patient_name, result_description FROM Patients JOIN StudyResults ON Patients.patient_id = StudyResults.patient_id WHERE StudyResults.result_description LIKE '%positive%' ORDER BY patient_name ASC;
